# Game

## FPS game combined with card game:
	- A FPS game combined with card game. In the FPS mode, you can use cards to call the affects and defend the enemy's card affects. And the card affects will influence the environments, the outlookings, the roles, the hero's ability, attributes and so on. Cards can be controlled and called by the number pad. 
	- And the game has multiplayer mode to support two player in the same hero, one to controll the motivation and attacks, while the other use cards to make other affects.
	- And it can connect to the mobile phones, so the cards can be controlled on the mobiles to be more convinients.
	- It can provide with pure card game mode.

